---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="404: Page Not Found | Leo Felcianas"
  description="The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 text-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-[#7aa2f7]">404</h1>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#c0caf5]">Page Not Found</h2>
      <p class="text-[#a9b1d6] mb-8">The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
      
      <div class="command-line p-4 bg-[#24283b] rounded-md w-full max-w-lg text-left">
        <p class="mb-2"><span class="command-prompt">$</span> find-page --url="<span class="text-[#f7768e]">not-found</span>"</p>
        <p class="text-[#f7768e]">Error: Page not found in directory</p>
        <p class="mb-2"><span class="command-prompt">$</span> suggest-action</p>
        <p>You can try the following:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-8 text-[#a9b1d6] mt-2">
          <li>Return to the <a href="/" class="text-[#7aa2f7] hover:underline">home page</a></li>
          <li>Check the URL for typos</li>
          <li>Contact me if you believe this is an error</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <a href="/" class="mt-6 px-6 py-2 bg-[#7aa2f7] text-[#1a1b26] rounded-md hover:bg-[#89b4fa] transition-colors font-medium">
        Return Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 